Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.46,0:33:01.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does this mean he looks like more than 50 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.62,0:33:03.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,60 years old?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.13,0:33:06.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.20,0:33:09.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does anyone ever say "looks like more than that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.60,0:33:10.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It has been said
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.57,0:33:12.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah thought so
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.50,0:33:15.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this deliberate...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.74,0:33:21.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is a sweater for people over 60 years old, right? \N -Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.78,0:33:24.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it not? \N -No
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.81,0:33:25.83,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Already too much
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.85,0:33:25.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.25,0:33:29.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,60 years old, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.64,0:33:28.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Still talking
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.62,0:33:32.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ishibashi Taka and others...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.49,0:33:35.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Born in Showa 36
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.69,0:33:38.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That is, more than...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.19,0:33:42.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,16 years older than me
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.13,0:33:45.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can 16 years older... oh I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.87,0:33:49.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're the same age as Tunnels?  \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.99,0:33:50.12,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So persistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.34,0:33:53.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.46,0:33:54.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No other questions at all \N -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.78,0:33:57.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Perhaps comedians just look young...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.86,0:33:59.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next at fourth place is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.39,0:34:14.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If an old man who suddenly instructed a segment on TV appeared a few days later as a director, his advice would be hastily taken to heart
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.33,0:34:22.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next in third place is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.85,0:34:30.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This theory introduced at the beginning of the program, with 66 character
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.08,0:34:34.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? The title is...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.55,0:34:37.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Crown program... ah
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.19,0:34:43.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next, the second highest number of words theory is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.49,0:35:01.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even if a skit is initially not very funny, if good comedians take over and write a part each, it will eventually become more interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.51,0:35:01.13,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's long  \N-Really long
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.66,0:35:06.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,By the way, this long theory originates with one of the member's of Knights
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.50,0:35:09.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.45,0:35:12.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello  \N-How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.31,0:35:16.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It begins with determining the content and writing the first section
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.19,0:35:22.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The skit is for a duo
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.07,0:35:26.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's about a taxi
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.47,0:35:30.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After the performance, there's a questionnaire
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.73,0:35:34.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It says "It's boring" or "same old stuff" or something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.74,0:35:37.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's good to get perspective
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.01,0:35:44.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As the skit that was initially performed live is not all that funny
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.89,0:35:52.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, the setup is changed
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.59,0:35:55.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The content is...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.50,0:36:00.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is a person who has always had a hard time getting a taxi
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.50,0:36:02.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The story of trying to stop a car
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.61,0:36:08.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An idiot is driving a cab, and while driving a cab he's dozing off
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.71,0:36:11.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The person trying to stop the car says "That's dangerous, is this driver ok?"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.55,0:36:15.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then the cab slams into a wall
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.00,0:36:16.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Boom, an accident
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.81,0:36:19.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then the man comes to the rescue
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.69,0:36:22.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Saying "Is everything okay?"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.56,0:36:23.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Where are you going?"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.89,0:36:26.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I'm not getting in"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.53,0:36:33.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The person selected to take over the next part of the skit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.27,0:36:36.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wow...okay
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.54,0:36:40.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Am I pioneer in segment optimization?\N  -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.31,0:36:41.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a nice title...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.76,0:36:46.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's worse is that after reading the beginning of the skit...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.32,0:36:50.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a bit difficult...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.95,0:36:52.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How to deal with the exchange...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.36,0:36:59.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, with much trouble, he finally manages to complete the second section
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.70,0:37:07.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, a collection of strong members continue the skit
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.74,0:37:11.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Well, in order to put the whole context together
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.57,0:37:15.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I did the best I could under the circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.03,0:37:19.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The performers of the skit are...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.26,0:37:21.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.09,0:37:23.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kamaitachi
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.35,0:37:26.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After all, it's been written by famous people
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.72,0:37:29.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If we can''t make it as funny as they want it to be
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.93,0:37:32.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We'll get criticized afterwards
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.83,0:37:35.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's true, there's a lot of details, the tone and so on
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.47,0:37:37.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}I'm full of anxiety...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.22,0:37:40.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, two days later
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.02,0:37:45.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In front of an audience that doesn't know anything, it's finally time to perform the skit
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.29,0:37:49.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How will the finished product turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.46,0:37:52.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Something has to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.28,0:37:56.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's a worry that maybe the next person won't be able to continue it on
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.12,0:37:58.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Super hard
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.23,0:37:59.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It has to become more interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.96,0:38:02.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It becomes the thing that each person themselves likes
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.91,0:38:11.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's so hard to get a cab
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.14,0:38:16.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah finally a taxi came, Taxi ~
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.69,0:38:19.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that car?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.94,0:38:23.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The driver is asleep, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.68,0:38:25.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.34,0:38:26.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.53,0:38:29.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Watch out, it's going to hit the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.95,0:38:33.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.88,0:38:36.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It completely became an accident
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.09,0:38:40.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.22,0:38:41.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.06,0:38:42.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting in!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.87,0:38:44.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't be a passenger, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.16,0:38:47.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The airbag is so slow...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.47,0:38:51.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You scared me  \N-You're similarly slow to react
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.99,0:38:55.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is bad. It's peak traffic time!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.34,0:38:58.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can this go back in?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.47,0:38:59.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.62,0:39:03.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The airbag, can it be stuffed back in?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.22,0:39:06.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Uh, I think they're mostly single-use
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.60,0:39:10.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, damn it, I wanted to drive a little longer
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.12,0:39:12.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But the car is finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.44,0:39:14.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The front is flattened
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.05,0:39:15.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.08,0:39:16.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You're not injured or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.91,0:39:17.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No i'm fine
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.92,0:39:19.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.35,0:39:22.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.01,0:39:23.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't get out
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.82,0:39:24.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.67,0:39:25.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm stuck
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.76,0:39:27.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.21,0:39:27.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.61,0:39:30.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, i'm out
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.45,0:39:31.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.44,0:39:35.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wow, seriously!? It's flattened
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.71,0:39:37.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.85,0:39:40.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wow, this...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.81,0:39:41.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.26,0:39:45.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did you shit yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.01,0:39:53.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, I have the vague memory of needing to go to the toilet before the accident happened
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.37,0:39:56.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The impact of the accident forced it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.56,0:40:03.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha ha
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.22,0:40:05.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's it coming out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.72,0:40:09.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I got out, this got out too
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.00,0:40:11.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's no laughing matter
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.23,0:40:13.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.86,0:40:18.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.32,0:40:19.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, there's a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.68,0:40:23.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's up? Lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.14,0:40:24.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, it's stuck
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.75,0:40:28.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's completely stuck inside
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.64,0:40:34.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.97,0:40:40.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are so many problems that I don't know where to start
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.13,0:40:43.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's start with the cat
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.32,0:40:44.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's poop, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.70,0:40:46.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.60,0:40:47.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Calling the police is the right thing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.94,0:40:49.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Suddenly normal words came out
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.31,0:40:51.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's true
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.16,0:40:57.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm in Akasaka 5-chome, I shit my pants
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.08,0:40:58.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's the use of this report?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.41,0:41:01.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seems like they won't come
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.47,0:41:02.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.15,0:41:05.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh... can you put this back?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.66,0:41:06.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.75,0:41:07.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.43,0:41:08.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How can you put {\i1}that{\i0} back
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.82,0:41:12.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not good to improperly report the accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.05,0:41:14.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But how should I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.13,0:41:15.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just report the facts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.76,0:41:21.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This statement is a bit difficult to make for the person involved in the accident itself
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.13,0:41:24.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's a cat.. can it be called a meow body accident
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.80,0:41:26.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It'll be seen as bullshit
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.17,0:41:30.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Combine that with the fact that I pooped in my pants
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.65,0:41:33.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Could it be called a human fecal accident? \N -Don't call it that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.86,0:41:37.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't get hung up on what to say exactly, just call them back
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.34,0:41:38.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.28,0:41:40.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,People are starting to gather
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.76,0:41:42.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.12,0:41:45.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Someone wants to be picked up
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.03,0:41:48.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I can't take passengers now
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.01,0:41:49.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A strange guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.64,0:41:52.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A strange guy on the same wavelength as this guy
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.31,0:41:56.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Meow body accident? That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.13,0:41:59.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Human fecal accident? Yes certainly
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.30,0:42:02.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this a pre-existing term? Am I the only one who doesn't know of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.09,0:42:04.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So it's impossible to carry passengers
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.47,0:42:07.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No passengers after an accident
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.17,0:42:09.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? You're saying the car is empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.49,0:42:12.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As I said, an accident has happened
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.08,0:42:14.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? You're saying the anus is also empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.69,0:42:18.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, it's something I can decide, maybe I can put it back
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.13,0:42:20.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Weirdoes and weirdoes have become tangled
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.30,0:42:23.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Weirdoes and weirdoes are fightings over a weird thing
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.61,0:42:25.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.71,0:42:26.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, are the police here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.64,0:42:30.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. Here it comes. It's great
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.33,0:42:32.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh? Words?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.06,0:42:36.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Weirdoes and weirdoes have become tangled
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.31,0:42:40.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Akiyama wrote this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.29,0:42:41.55,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Akiyama's part
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.17,0:42:39.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Weirdoes and weirdoes are fightings over a weird thing
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.26,0:42:41.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Strange people and strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.89,0:42:44.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.06,0:42:48.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,My name is Riverbank Ghost Light
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.08,0:42:49.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Riverbank Ghost Light？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.51,0:42:50.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's definitely Akiyama's work
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.19,0:42:53.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not in this form, but i've worked as a singer previously
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.84,0:42:55.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What happened all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.81,0:42:59.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But Riverbank Ghost Light has not yet debuted
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.59,0:43:02.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So i'm working hard as a driver to support my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.89,0:43:04.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You are developing too fast
